-- Germany to Build New Center to Manage Cyber Defense, Bild Zeitung Reports
-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 2010-12-28T07:52:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-28/germany-to-establish-defense-against-hackers-internet-spies-bild-says.html
The German government is planning to
build a new “cyber center” that will coordinate defense
measures against hackers and internet-spies,  Bild  reported,
citing a spokesman for the interior ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:  Ragnhild Kjetland  in
Frankfurt at   rkjetland@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story: Vidya Root at
   vroot@bloomberg.net  